# Fullstack Engineer

More info at https://www.datacamp.com/careers/164840

## Responsibilities

We are looking for a talented full-stack software engineer to focus on improving and expanding our learning product. You should love to build apps and solve technical challenges.
Our stack currently includes:
- AngularJS
- NodeJS
- Ruby on Rails
- R
- Python
- Docker
- we’re using AWS for hosting.

## The ideal candidate

- Loves building apps, both front-end and back-end, that scale to hundreds of thousands of users
- Has built cool stuff before (no need to apply if you didn’t)
- Is interested in data science
- Works well in a team
- Has experience with (multiple) new web development frameworks
- Experience in data science is a plus

## What we offer
- A salary, of course
- Stock options in an early stage start-up with a lot of growth potential
- Flexibility: Want to work from home? Want to take a week off to go on holidays? Want to work different hours? We can work something out
- Exciting job that will offer you technical challenges on a daily basis
- Opportunity to work in an internationally focused, fast-paced technology start-up
